Class MultipleValueArgument

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.analysis.util.Argument
      • org.hps.analysis.util.MultipleValueArgument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<String>

    public class MultipleValueArgument
extends Argument
implements Iterable<String>
    MultipleValueArgument represents a command line argument that allows for a multiple instances of itself. It is an implementation of Argument.
